name: Overflow (itch) (Bird Brains)
description:
This rabbits house is being flooded. Guide this rabbit to safety by using the SPACE key on the keyboard or by using the LEFT MOUSE BUTTON to make the rabbit jump forward. If you are on a mobile device, tap the screen to make the rabbit jump. 

Time your jumps carefully as dangerous traps like buzzsaws and more buzzsaws that were apparently installed in the burrow for security reasons line the path ahead. Don't take too long though as the rushing water will catch up to you for a nasty bath. 

This is our first game under Bird Brains Studio and we hoped you had a lot of fun with the game we made.
